channel.title: Help with a few things please?
channel.description:
I'm using TrisidiaX V2. How do you fix ::noclip. you keep logging out. Underneath it in commands.java, it says c.logout or something, what do i put there?
How do I change the currency of a shop? Like level points shop or donator store. And the prices of it, It's not in prices.txt.

item.title: Help with a few things please?
item.dc:creator: @PvPXile PvPXile
item.description:
@PvPXile wrote:

Jesus christ, you just told yourself thee answer. Under the method it says c.logout. Wouldn’t you think it would appropriate to remove this? Then you would not “logout”.

To change the currency of a shop, you will have to make it accept a special value. There are hundreds of guides on it.

Read full topic
item.source: Help with a few things please?
